questions.quote: Hey, I'm sorry, I- you know, I, I thought you knew.  You got any meat?
Anyway, let me tell you why I called. When I took over here last month, I reviewed what was in development,and it was pretty much same old, same old.
She's an... etymologist. You know, bees, flies, gnats. W-What about you?
All you got is instant coffee? Why don't you get some real coffee?
Well , as I said this type of thing is very common in show business
Oh, the remote! Okay, I'm just gonna put it on top of the television...
I know. No awkward pauses. Probably the reason we never fooled around..
You know, I was thinking if you're not busy, maybe I can get my meal today?
This is a fantastic place! I always thought it was a meat packing plant!
Oh...it's daylight. It won't take you that long. Just make a clean break.
